{"tid":960471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新年快樂!!!","createTime":"2018-12-29T12:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T12:39:25.000Z","uid":228328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13e033e6c12b66757269998e2bbe0bfe72206103","tid":960471,"uid":228328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"好多嘢，都唔係理所當然<br />\n我最感謝係我屋企人，佢地喺我心、生命中都係第一。<br />\n媽媽雖然長氣，冇記性，但佢都係關心我<br />\n爸爸喺我最愛，無得挑剔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啊哥細佬成日都蝦我，但無你地又點會有搞笑的氣氛。<br />\n喺 我病、失戀、成績差時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地都絞盡腦汁幫我同鼓勵我。<br />\n真係好多謝你地<br />\n<br />\n希望新一年大家都健健康康，我愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c96adcfa8658f10102a57d43ecaaedf9149135","tid":960471,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"你未多謝我喎"},{"pid":"36f57c7ac227540161445a667684f375f6f6eeb3","tid":960471,"uid":228328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c96adcfa8658f10102a57d43ecaaedf9149135","tid":960471,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"你未多謝我喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"多謝你睇完 #dogxm"}]}